examples.en: TV violence perverts the minds of young children.

examples.en: I keep getting obscene phone calls from some sick pervert.

examples.en: Forcing everyone to vote for the dictator perverts the very idea of democracy.

examples.en: Genetic scientists are often accused of perverting nature.
